These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-1::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, whist, bridge, backgammon
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, gardening, puzzles, writing
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, dog, frog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, golf, cycling, handball
 1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
 2. the person playing whist is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 7. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 8. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 9. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
11. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |   4   |
| Game    | bridge   | whist       | mah-jongg | backgammon   |
| Hobby        | gardening    | writing  | puzzles      | photography |
| Pet         | frog      | chinchilla | dog         | cat   |
| Sport   | volleyball | golf       | cycling        | handball   |

