.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, electrician, photographer, police-officer
4 different games are played: canasta, whist, monopoly, poker
4 different pets are kept: mouse, goat, ferret, frog
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, bongani, dunhill, vegafina
1. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the electrician is the person playing canasta##1
3. the dunhill-smoker is the photographer##1
4. the bartender is between the person playing whist and the aristoff-smoker##2
5. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
6. the owner of the frog is the vegafina-smoker##1
7. the owner of the mouse is on the far right##1
8. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |       3        |      4       |
| Job           | electrician | bartender | police-officer | photographer |
| Game   | canasta  | monopoly | whist         | poker      |
| Pet         | ferret      | goat    | frog         | mouse   |
| Cigar     | aristoff         | bongani    | vegafina          | dunhill         |

