.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, bellflower, marigold, aconite
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, board-games, sudoku, reading
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, grey, black, coral
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, ice-hockey, volleyball
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person who growsmarigold##1
 2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 4. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 5. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 8. the person who likes amber is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
 9. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
10. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Flower          | bellflower | aconite  | daisy | marigold      |
| Hobby   | traveling       | reading    | board-games      | sudoku      |
| Color           | coral     | amber     | grey         | black   |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | cricket | cycling     | volleyball |

