3. the photographer is the fan of country##1
4. the fan of electronic is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes white is the fan of country##1
6. the person who likes red is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
8. the videographer is between the person driving the tram and the person who likes brown##2
9. the librarian is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4       |
| Job           | lawyer     | videographer | librarian | photographer |
| Music-Genre   | electronic     | dubstep       | r&b      | country   |
| Color   | red   | emerald   | brown    | white       |
| Transport           | tram | airplane        | subway    | taxi        |

