 7. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the journalist##3
 8. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the pilot##1
 9. the teacher is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
10. the person who growsbegonia is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who growstulip##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | almond-milk | fanta     | cola       |
