 6. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 8. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 9. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's birthday is in march##1
10. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
11. the person who likes grey is the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3       |     4     |
| Hobby         | chess      | video-games | sudoku       | drawing   |
| Color   | grey     | black | blood-red | coral |
| Birthday   | november    | october     | september        | march       |
| Sport     | snowboarding | weightlifting   | parkour   | golf       |

