.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, blueberry, radish, watermelon
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, indonesian, spanish, thai
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, mauve, apricot, coral
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, 7up, coffee
 1. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the japanese##1
 3. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 4. the indonesian is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
 5. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
 6. the person who likes azure is between the indonesian and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 7. the person who likes apricot is the thai##1
 8. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
 9. the person eating radish is the indonesian##1
10. the person who likes azure is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| Food          | blueberry | watermelon   | radish   | artichoke |
| Nationality           | japanese   | spanish     | indonesian   | thai |
| Color   | mauve    | azure    | coral   | apricot   |
| Beverage         | iced-tea    | hot-chocolate | coffee | 7up    |

 